    <title>重新搭建vps</title>
    <link href="https://sdjk.github.io/2018/10/21/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAvps/"/>
    <id>https://sdjk.github.io/2018/10/21/重新搭建vps/</id>
    <published>2018-10-20T16:11:51.452Z</published>
    <updated>2018-10-20T17:13:20.125Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="重新搭建vps"><a href="#重新搭建vps" class="headerlink" title="重新搭建vps"></a>重新搭建vps</h1><blockquote><p>实现下载文件到Google Drive，使用emby点播视频<br>环境：Ubuntu 18.04 x64</p></blockquote><h2 id="SS-1"><a href="#SS-1" class="headerlink" title="SS^1"></a>SS<a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-libev" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^1</a></h2><ul><li>重置服务</li><li><p>使用命令清除ssh连接记录</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -R Server IP Address</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>开始安装</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install shadowsocks-libev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改配置文件</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>启动服务</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl start shadowsocks-libev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><a id="more"></a><ul><li><p>是否有开启==bbr==</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lsmod | grep bbr</span><br><span class="line">tcp_bbr                20480  32</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重启服务器 </p></li></ul><h2 id="aria2-2"><a href="#aria2-2" class="headerlink" title="aria2^2"></a>aria2<a href="https://github.com/aria2/aria2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^2</a></h2><blockquote><p>vps下载工具</p></blockquote><ul><li><p>安装</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install aria2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>查看版本</p>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aria2c -v</span><br><span class="line">aria2 version 1.33.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="运行"><a href="#运行" class="headerlink" title="运行"></a>运行</h3><ul><li><p>WebUI-Aria2运行如下命令</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aria2c --enable-rpc --rpc-listen-all -D</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>AriaNg运行如下命令</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aria2c --enable-rpc --rpc-listen-all --rpc-allow-origin-all -D</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>每一次服务器重启都需要键入</p></li></ul><h2 id="WebUI-Aria2-3"><a href="#WebUI-Aria2-3" class="headerlink" title="WebUI-Aria2^3"></a>WebUI-Aria2<a href="https://github.com/ziahamza/webui-aria2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^3</a></h2><blockquote><p>Aria2的图形管理界面，也可使用<a href="https://github.com/mayswind/AriaNg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AriaNg</a></p></blockquote><ul><li><p>需要先安装web服务，选择==Nginx==（或Apache）</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>进入==Nginx==的根目录安装</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /var/www/html</span><br><span class="line">git clone http://github.com/ziahamza/webui-aria2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>把文件转移到根目录</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd webui-aria2</span><br><span class="line">mv * /var/www/html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开地址</p>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://Server IP Address/docs/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="Emby-4"><a href="#Emby-4" class="headerlink" title="Emby^4"></a>Emby<a href="https://emby.media/linux-server.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^4</a></h2><blockquote><p>多媒体点播程序，也可使用<a href="https://www.plex.tv/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PLEX</a></p></blockquote><ul><li><p>下载deb包</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://github.com/MediaBrowser/Emby.Releases/releases/download/3.5.2.0/emby-server-deb_3.5.2.0_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dpkg -i emby-server-deb_3.5.2.0_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开地址</p>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://Server IP Address:8096</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><ul><li><p>重启服务</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo service emby-server start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="rclone"><a href="#rclone" class="headerlink" title="rclone"></a>rclone</h2><blockquote><p>网盘工具</p></blockquote><h3 id="安装-5"><a href="#安装-5" class="headerlink" title="安装^5"></a>安装<a href="https://rclone.org/install/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^5</a></h3><ul><li><p>安装unzip</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install unzip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>下载并解压，进入操作目录</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -O https://downloads.rclone.org/rclone-current-linux-amd64.zip</span><br><span class="line">unzip rclone-current-linux-amd64.zip</span><br><span class="line">cd rclone-*-linux-amd64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>复制 binary file</p>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo cp rclone /usr/bin/</span><br><span class="line">sudo chown root:root /usr/bin/rclone</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod 755 /usr/bin/rclone</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装 manpage</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/share/man/man1</span><br><span class="line">sudo cp rclone.1 /usr/local/share/man/man1/</span><br><span class="line">sudo mandb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="Google-Drive授权-6"><a href="#Google-Drive授权-6" class="headerlink" title="Google Drive授权^6"></a>Google Drive授权<a href="https://rclone.org/drive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^6</a></h3><blockquote><p>使用教育版，无限空间<a href="https://www.erbuxiu.com/0044295.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^7</a></p></blockquote><ul><li><p>运行配置文件</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rclone config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>按照官方教程进行配置</p></li><li>需要打开<code>http://127.0.0.1:53682/auth</code>进行授权</li><li><p>可以使用ssh隧道，用本地电脑做授权</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh root@IP Address -L 8888:localhost:53682</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开地址进行授权</p>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://localhost:8888/auth</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="挂载-8"><a href="#挂载-8" class="headerlink" title="挂载^8"></a>挂载<a href="https://rclone.org/commands/rclone_mount/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^8</a></h3><ul><li><p>创建一个缓存文件夹</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /var</span><br><span class="line">mkdir rcloneCache</span><br><span class="line">/var/rcloneCache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>创建一个挂载目录</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/var/google</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>运行命令进行挂载</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rclone mount google: /var/google  --allow-other --umask 0027 --cache-dir /var/rcloneCache --dir-cache-time 1h --vfs-cache-max-age 1h --vfs-read-chunk-size 10M --buffer-size 32M --vfs-read-chunk-size-limit 32M --vfs-cache-mode writes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>参考官方和服务器自行调整</li></ul></li><li><p>尝试命令</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rclone mount google: /var/google  --allow-other --umask 0027 --cache-dir /var/rcloneCache --dir-cache-time 1h --vfs-read-chunk-size 10M --vfs-read-chunk-size-limit 32M --vfs-cache-mode writes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>尝试命令：</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rclone mount google: /var/google --allow-other --cache-dir /var/rcloneCache --dir-cache-time 20m --vfs-read-chunk-size 10M --vfs-read-chunk-size-limit 128M --vfs-cache-mode writes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使用命令：</p><pre><code class="shell">rclone mount onedrive: /var/onedrive --allow-other --cache-dir /var/rcloneCache --dir-cache-time 20m --vfs-read-chunk-size 10M --vfs-read-chunk-size-limit 128M --vfs-cache-mode writes </code></pre></li></ul><ul><li>使用命令<code>df -h</code>查看挂载状况<a href="http://www.runoob.com/linux/linux-comm-df.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^9</a></li><li>使用命令<code>free -m</code>查看内存状况<a href="http://www.runoob.com/linux/linux-comm-free.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^10</a></li><li>使用命令<code>du -h</code>查看各文件目录占用硬盘大小<a href="http://www.runoob.com/linux/linux-comm-du.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">^11</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h1 id=&quot;重新搭建vps&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#重新搭建vps&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;重新搭建vps&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;重新搭建vps&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;实现下载文件到Google Drive，使用emby点播视频&lt;br&gt;环境：Ubuntu 18.04 x64&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;SS-1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#SS-1&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;SS^1&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;SS&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-libev&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;^1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;重置服务&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;使用命令清除ssh连接记录&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ssh-keygen -R Server IP Address&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;开始安装&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo apt update&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo apt install shadowsocks-libev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;修改配置文件&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo vim /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;启动服务&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo systemctl start shadowsocks-libev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
